---
// Self-hosted narrated walkthrough of the two showcase beats (find-a-file + summarize,
// then reply → propose → approve → book/invite → file a brief), in Nora's own voice.
// Narrated → click-to-play with sound (no autoplay/mute/loop); poster + controls.
const src = `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}nora-demo.mp4`;
const poster = `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}nora-demo-poster.jpg`;
---
<div class="mt-8">
  <div class="relative aspect-video w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-[var(--color-deepink)] shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(15,26,36,0.18)]">
    <video
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
      src={src}
      poster={poster}
      controls
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
      aria-label="Nora demo, narrated — she finds a file and summarizes it, then drafts a reply, proposes a meeting, and only books and files it after you approve."
    ></video>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/60">
    A ~60-second walkthrough, narrated by Nora: she finds the right file and summarizes it, then
    drafts a reply, proposes the meeting, and only books, invites, and files the brief
    <em>after you approve</em> — always from her own identity, never as you. <span class="text-ink/45">Tap to play with sound.</span>
  </p>
</div>
